YOU WILL ALWAYS BE IN OUR HEARTS.
ALL OUR LOVE KAREN, MUM AND DAD"Ž
╠In loving memory of
Elsie Margaret Hazel Potter
1931 - 2016
and the many happy hours
she spent here

And her close friend
Mary Gwendoline Beattie
1940 - 2016
Who also loved
Titchwell and Norfolk"ę
ŽIN MEMORY OF
PETER SANDERS
(1944 - 2012)
Beloved Husband, Dad and Grandad
He loved Norfolk and this Reserve
Now free as a bird

In Loving Memory of
Peter Sanders
Beloved brother
Take wings and soar"▌
